## GLOBAL SCREEN RULES (APPLY TO ALL)

| Rule              | Spec                          |
| ----------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Layout            | 12-column grid                |
| Sidebar           | Fixed (240–280px)             |
| Top bar           | Sticky                        |
| Primary action    | Top-right only                |
| Secondary actions | Inline / row-level            |
| Save behavior     | Explicit only                 |
| Errors            | Inline + summary              |
| Keyboard          | All primary actions reachable |

