# 1. DASHBOARD (READ-ONLY)

### Purpose

Provide **situational awareness**. No state mutation.

---

### Data Blocks

| Block            | Content                                               | Behavior          |
| ---------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- | ----------------- |
| KPI Summary      | Active workers, jobs today, total paid, total top-ups | Read-only         |
| Alerts           | Failed payments, pending reviews                      | Click → deep link |
| Job Status Table | Job ID, skill, workers, status                        | Sortable          |
| Time Context     | “Today / This week”                                   | Filter only       |

---

### Actions

| Action       | Location  | Rule            |
| ------------ | --------- | --------------- |
| View details | Row click | Navigation only |
| Refresh      | Top bar   | Manual          |

🚫 No create/edit actions allowed

